<select
  value={priorityId}
  onChange={(e) => setPriorityId(e.target.value)}
  required
>
  <option value="" disabled>
    ⚡ Öncelik seçin
  </option>
  {priorities.map((pri) => (
    <option key={pri.priorityId} value={pri.priorityId}>
      {pri.name}
    </option>
  ))}
</select>
